{"tid":505823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男女搭計程車當場車震　司機尷尬看活春宮","createTime":"2017-12-21T14:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T04:32:10.000Z","uid":10958,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b8dcdda2edf504485cae0ec751c104abba8f49cf","tid":505823,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>男女搭計程車當場車震　司機尷尬看活春宮</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rtnvideo1.appledaily.com.tw/mcp/encode/2017/12/21/3509280/1263321_360p.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frtnvideo1.appledaily.com.tw%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F3509280%2F1263321_360p.mp4&d=m6%2BIrinw8%2B9tR7N%2FW6xkEKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c5cf6b9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://rtnvideo1.appledaily.com.tw/mcp/encode/2017/12/21/3509280/1263321_360p.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n這絕非計程車AV系列，這是真實畫面！俄羅斯莫斯科一名計程車司機，日前載到一對男女乘客，沒想到這對男女把計程車當成摩鐵，當場車震，讓司機超級尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這名「我只是個認真工作的計程車司機」表示，當天他載在這對男女乘客，要求載他們回家，原本路程只有一小段，但這對男女上車後，竟馬上寬衣解帶，女子跨坐在男子身上，兩人馬上展開活春宮。司機尷尬地看到兩人車震，他原本想要保持鎮定，假裝沒看見，但這對男女隨後卻要求司機下車10分鐘，因為他們想要完成「私人時間」。<br />\n<br />\n這時司機怒了，馬上拒絕情侶的要求，並對他們咆嘯：「你們瘋了嗎，要我下車然後你們在車上做愛？？去酒吧做那事兒吧！」據悉這對男女付了約新台幣200元的車資後，下車離開並前往酒吧，但司機還持續在車內抱怨：「他們在要我車內X，還要我離開車子10分鐘，是怎樣，最好他是能撐10分鐘啦！」最後司機也把這段行車紀錄畫面上傳YouTube。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171221/640_0667e4c0d74cf77ae48c9b2b84cb8f94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171221%2F640_0667e4c0d74cf77ae48c9b2b84cb8f94.jpg&h=099dbd47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">男女搭計程車當場車震，司機尷尬看活春宮。翻自《太陽報》</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171221/640_3056f7096e3a5dba42689631dde9d6cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171221%2F640_3056f7096e3a5dba42689631dde9d6cb.jpg&h=c470a7d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">這名「我只是個認真工作的計程車司機」真的超不爽。翻自《太陽報》</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20171221/1263321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20171221%2F1263321&d=m6%2BIrinw8%2B9tR7N%2FW6xkEKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a9c56a59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20171221%2F1263321&h=b29610d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20171221/1263321</a>"},{"pid":"856d4cf1467a0fa743b3ac331123105d817a1008","tid":505823,"uid":56729,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"自己無份又真係幾尷尬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630f6282f0c6ad1ef05b22bcd13a029291c21ad2","tid":505823,"uid":71257,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:19:02.000Z","msg":"手機響鈴"},{"pid":"1b582a3519200c6646f3b2ffb3cca6a1d79e9f88","tid":505823,"uid":3647,"like":29,"dislike":8,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手機響鈴</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/224349_4e5ddc2426d322b9f0300276abd1bb09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F224349_4e5ddc2426d322b9f0300276abd1bb09.jpg&h=a6664afe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15b72f91d442ac32c7b244e1e7bab236613bdb35","tid":505823,"uid":11254,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"FAKE TAXI"},{"pid":"0bd9b2a39732f74e5f801c5ff26b4c2663ab8aae","tid":505823,"uid":23445,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"司機:I know a quiet place nearby"},{"pid":"4f3fb4f7720170798ee07368e49d20404100e37e","tid":505823,"uid":82394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯+1分"},{"pid":"dfd08965